    %h4 About
    .p.about.pull-right By reducing the number of keys needed to type to 10 we remove the need for a board of keys,  and now just need a button assigned to each finger; this could be a glove, or some other hand held device. Without a board we no longer need a table,  giving us much greater freedom to where we can input text.  But what about the mouse?  The latest device I have created has a gyroscope in the right hand device which provides a natural way to control a pointer.
